address1: Plot No. 1, Maruti Udyog Joint Venture Complex
longBusinessSummary: Bharat Seats Limited manufactures and sells seating systems and interior components for the automotive and surface transport industries in India. It offers seats for four-wheeler, two-wheeler, and railways chair car; carpets; roof and windshield modeling products; and two-wheeler frame parts. The company was incorporated in 1986 and is based in Gurugram, India.
